Detailed Description

Describes an application error.

A report has a type, which is one of

TYPE_CRASH application crash. Information about the crash is stored in crashInfo. TYPE_ANR application not responding. Information about the ANR is stored in anrInfo. TYPE_NONE uninitialized instance of ApplicationErrorReport.
